CypressError: Timed out retrying after 4000ms: The command was expected to run against origin `https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com` but the application is at origin `https://www.google.com`.

This commonly happens when you have either not navigated to the expected origin or have navigated away unexpectedly.

Using `cy.origin()` to wrap the commands run on `https://www.google.com` will likely fix this issue.

`cy.origin('https://www.google.com', () => {`
`  <commands targeting https://www.google.com go here>`
`})`
